  "body": "When I try to make all steps in CONTRIBUTING.md, I am facing with an issue. Here is the steps I follow\r\ngit clone git@github.com:ethereum-optimism/optimism.git\r\n```\r\ncd optimism\r\nyarn install\r\nnvm use\r\nyarn clean\r\nyarn build\r\ncd ops\r\nexport COMPOSE_DOCKER_CLI_BUILD=1 # these environment variables significantly speed up build time\r\nexport DOCKER_BUILDKIT=1\r\ndocker-compose build\r\n```\r\nWhen I complete the above steps, I don't get any error and it completes successfully.\r\nThen, I run this command:\r\n`docker-compose up`\r\n\r\nI get this error loop from batch-submitter-service:\r\n<img width=\"705\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-08-25 at 11 04 10\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29749723/186613024-1bafa982-6332-4dfc-bb2f-2b5eaf300448.png\">\r\n\r\nAlso, I just wonder how can I reach user interface. Which port should I use?\r\n\r\n",
